\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 No. No. I suppose we came i
