\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Oh yes. Yes, yes, yes. I mean to say you - you were taught to be tolerant t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5709036\charrsid2370612 
