\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Our quarrels. Well I suppose we had our quarrels out of - out of the way when they weren't about - I should assume anyway.
