dy keeping crow see if there's any policemen about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Was it against the law?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Oh yes. Pitch and toss is. Gambling. In - in a public place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 So it was the women who came round?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 They come round with their clothes}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid798420\charrsid2370612 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 pegs all the lot of them. All dyed osiers tops you know, dyed osiers. The plume}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid798420\charrsid2370612  - the p}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 
lume was osier. Dyed - it was magenta and that sort of thing you know, yellow or magenta and come round with bunches of that for sale you know. Try it on. You've seen them often.
