\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Well - there wasn't much to choose - you - if y
ou can imagine, oh no need to imagine you know there are - streets and streets of houses of terrace type houses you walk down and you can pick out the - the humble and the less - less humble. Or the rich or the less rich. Living in the same vicinity by lo
oking at their windows and their doors. You can tell - or if they've got a small front garden, manner in which they keep their -
