\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 It - it's personal to them, and the manner in which they live isn't it. Theref
ore you can't say that - that's person's richer than the other one. They're probably all of them - they could be all on the same income group but - but - this is where the snobbishness comes in, if - in the extension or expansion of the borough into more 
s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid798420\charrsid2370612 a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 
lubrious areas what happens. Those that have got the where with all move out. Becomes suburbia doesn't it. Therefore the - they come what they call toffee nosed I use these expressions, you'll have to excuse them won't you.
