I - I also - I'm also - in - embodying that - I'm including that in it because my father you see moved out from - a four terrace house and - in Portsmouth to a place that had been freshly built in a rural area. He's still within - with
in - you know, stones throw of his work you might say or within reasonable distance of his work, of course there weren't any electric tramcars in those days, they were horse-drawn.
