Yes, that is so. Yes, that is so. Yes. So you see - when you became - become more affluent you - so you take the stride up don't you, in other words you - you'll be getting rid of that old rain}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid798420\charrsid2370612 
-}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 hood in a minute - you'll be getting rid of that old rain}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid798420\charrsid2370612 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 
hood in a minute and getting a - a leather shoe. You see. I mean -
