I think they accepted people that they - in - came across together. You know, if one - if one particular type of people were there with father it was hers. They had - well, of course that comes back to a further - a prev
ious question about associates. You come back on the same thing really don't you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 But you think they were the same degree of accepting?
