\insrsid798420\charrsid2370612  - for children - for attendances. And if you got attendanc}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 es, w
ell - and punctuality I - I got - as a matter of fact I daresay I could show you a - one of my old prizes which has got that - in the front \{ILLEGIBLE\} attendance and so forth. So - so -
