\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Oh I - I don't think they were so - perfect in that respect. Mind you - they taught us the - the three R's, rea}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
