\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Well I suppose we did gang up
 a bit you know, because - you could say - well gang up to this extent, that children with - lived in - within one street, would - perhaps congregate. After school time, so they're - so that normally I suppose we would have congregated in the playground a
t playtime. That - that's - that's my obvious - rply to that, because I - I can't really - imagine us doing anything different.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 So you can't remember any particular children who were left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 No, I can't. No. No, I can't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 The school you went on to after that school, did you go on to the Higher Grade School from there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 
No. No. No, this - this - the - I've got another school to come through now first, but - coming back to this - this particular era - this week was the anniversa
ry of Queen Victoria, or this last week. I marched from this school - about a mile and a half, two miles - up to - Stansall recreation ground as it was then, its not Alexandra Park in Portsmouth, where we had races and all that sort of thing on they 1897 
- Queen - Queen Victoria's Jubillee, and I received a beaker, china beaker for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Have you still got it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 
Did I give that to Geoff only a few weeks ago wasn't it? And - walk - that's walking - you don't know Portsmouth at all do you? No. Well fro
m - Flattenbury anyway walking right through - right up Commercial Road right out to - right out more - more or less out in the country, about - two miles I should think roughly. To - this Stansall recreation ground as it was, and it was more or less a m}
{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid798420\charrsid2370612 ea}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 dow, as is now a park you see, with all the - amenities and so forth.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Did all the children in the schools in Portsmouth go too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Oh we - we had - I do remember this 'cos I - we were in a race - three boys and the girls were drivers, with ribbons 
you know attached to you, you know. And that was the Ju - Diamond Jubilee celebrations for the schools. I remember - I was five years old then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 How old were you when you changed schools then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 I should say I was about eight and a half, to - to ni
ne. We moved out to Milton. So - I changed schools, I went to Francis Avenue school, which was a newer school built not aw - all that farther from the station, you could say - that Harold Road school where I went to first was that side of the station, Fra
ncis Avenue school was over there that side and about - ten minutes walk between the two really.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 So that when you moved you had quite a long walk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 I still had a long walk to come - come back - from the new area that had been - built out of Milton, to come -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Did you still walk every day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 On your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Oh yes. Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Was that a boys school as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Well, yes, you see, there - there weren't the co-educational as they are now. They had the boys por
tion - the girls portion, they were adjacent but a - but apart.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 The new school was a board school as well was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Would you go home to dinner then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Yes. I went home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 It was quite a long walk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Yes. But - no - no school meals in those days you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Did you like that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Oh I liked it well enough, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 How did you feel about the teachers at that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Well I was - I can remember - Mr Bath, that was his name, I can picture him now. At 
this school we had the workhouse boys came to this school, it was adjacent to Milton you see, and that was the nearest school to them. We had them there. And they were a rough handful, I remember one - one boy particularly picking up inkwell and throwing 
it at the - at this - the teacher, and - and Mr Bath chasing him around the desks, you know, those little low desks, and - cutting him across the behind with a stick. And that's - that's one instance I was going say about punishment just now.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Were you astounded at that behaviour?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 
In a way I suppose we accepted it. I suppose we thought that they were - I suppose we were getting a little bit - toffee nosed perhaps and - and we - accepted them as - part and parcel of the ruff'uns of the school. But 
still, nevertheless - they all had to have their education.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Did you tend not to mix with them in playtime?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 I can't remember much about the playing there because - as I say - we didn't have much time for playing about and - and - I suppose normal
ly we had our little bit of drill out in the playground and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid798420\charrsid2370612 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612  a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid798420\charrsid2370612  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 kick about with the ball of course. Ball was always in the - in the playground.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Were there gangs and groups in that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 No, I should imagine - if there were - if there were gang
s, they would - we would gang up - the - workhouse boys would go - their way and we would go ours, you know that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Did your parents show more interest in your school then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Well my father was - as I told you before, he was a very bus
y man, he wasn't - available - for that, but my mother was a - busy woman bringing up a family and she also hadn't got all that time - to know how each individual member of the family was doing. When you look back on it I can really visualize that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Do you remember the teachers singling out children for special treatment at that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 
No, I don't think so. As I say - the - one or two of these workhouse boys I remember distinctly this particular incident I was just - recalled. That also - could b
ring back to mind that some of these boys were more or less - put aside, and held - tried to discipline them a bit, which was obvious, that had to be done
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 The next move in schools was when you went to Plymouth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Next I went to Plymouth, yes. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 What sort of schools did you go there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 I went to Salisbury Road school for - the - first - beginning of the winter term or - no, autumn term they term it these days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 That was another board school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 That was another board school for t
hree months. During that time I passed my examination - the eleven plus I would term it now, I passed for the higher grade school. And I went to the higher grade school, Regent Street. High - higher grade school 'til I - went to my apprentice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Did that school seem very different from the ones you'd been to before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Oh absolutely. Oh not the board school, you mean -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 I meant the higher grade school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Higher grade school, yes, definitely. You were in a grade, you were in a - well it - it's 
selective, I'll put it that way shall I. 'Cos you had - you had similar - characteristics to the present day schooling of - well I suppose a technical school. Inasmuch as we did woodwork - we did iron - you know - metal work. We also did - all the - we ha
d a commercial class for -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 You did science too didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 
We did science, yes, yes, yes, we had a good lab, we had a fine science master too. That I remember very well, and - as I - I believe I said in preambles before that - we did wonderfully 
well and that school - is now Sutton High School there Some of the - my classmates - and I and - can remember - reach - reached the high degree. One was knighted and - and several more - reached the top.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Were you living near that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Not too
 far away at that first time, but then we moved from - where we were - were handy at the board school I first went to while we were there. We had move from there - out to - in the estate was being built - on the outskirts of Plymouth, adjacent to the Temp
le side. Of course I had a fair walk then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 How long would it take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Half an hour. Previously it only took me about - ten minutes or quarter of an hour the other way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 You went home for dinners did you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Yes. Yes. Yes. Oh not always. 
No, not always, when we moved out to Peveral I remember - often used to have - a few pence to go and get myself a - Cornish pasty or something like that you know, and - have a roam round or - go do perhaps a bit of shopping for mother. So when we - I went
 back like home at teatime, take home a bit of shopping for her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 How did you feel about the teachers at that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Oh they were - they were a - they were a class on their own really. They were they were - people - distinctly - a class - for the
 - for the particular training that they were - they were for. And - they were strict. I know my - headmaster Mr Lethbridge, he was a - I picture him now, he just looked like Shakespeare did beard and all, but he was a - he was a thorough gentleman and we
 
had our - thing we don't have in the board schools mind you, we had - the - morning - parade you know in the hall and - prayers and - so forth. We had an art master, we had a science master, we had - we had the lot really, as - as - still prevails now in 
the schools. In the - in the - in the secondary modern schools particularly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Did they emphasise things there such as manners or tidiness as being important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Oh yes. Yes, definitely. Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 And punctuality?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Punctuality, yes. I thi
nk - I think you could say all the ethics of good living try to install it, and also - now what would I say, spirit of esprit de }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5785297\charrsid2370612 c}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid798420\charrsid2370612 
oeur}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 How about ways of speaking, did you have to speak correctly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Oh you had, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 I remember you telling me you went in for elocution?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Well - I know my father did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Didn't you say you did as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 
Well I had a little but not much. But I - I could - I could recite once upon a time but - you know, The Revenge - that sort of thing, but still -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 How about punishment at that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Well that - that - you can have that too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Was that corporal punishment?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Yes, corporal punishment.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 What sort of things would you have to do to get caned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Well I suppose tell lies or anything like that you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 The same sort of thing as before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Were your parents more interested in your school work at that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Well of course then - I'm talking myself individually now, I suppose - my parents were - really my fa
ther particularly I suppose was getting interested in me, inasmuch as that - I was growing up and I would have to come out into the world, and therefore he would - be - interested to that extent, to know how I was getting on. 'Cos I used to have to do hom
ework then. And I used to go back to school and do - do - night school as well, in the later stages when I was in higher forms. Or classes as they were then, they weren't forms but classes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 I remember you saying that staying on at school you felt slightly different.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 
Oh yes, you - you developed - you developed - well I developed particularly I suppose a - a sense of - responsibility to myself and my - my parents. Inasmuch as - although I didn't get what I wanted to do - I felt that I was going to b
e independent if I could, and that's the feeling we had. I suppose that's - some what can I say, a - a spirit that - one doesn't always - see in - children these days. Whereas as long as they can - get what they can out of their parents they're satisfied 
and that's that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 You were more concerned about the future?
