\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 No, no, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 If it is it's one of bad feeling.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Well we enjoyed ourselves social 
life, I - I did have the pleasure of having a few - few waltz steps with - what we - what was eventually Lady Aster, when I was - about - I was eighteen, nineteen, just going on nineteen then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Were there any other things that you were involved in apar
t from the walking and the social club, I suppose that would take your time all up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Well, it took up most of my time really. I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 What about before you started that, because that was 1910, between 1908 and 1910?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Well - actually - I suppose I could say that - I'm more or less involved with St. Gabriel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5785297\charrsid2370612 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 
s football club, that's a church - church football club you see, playing with them and then - the summertime playing cricket. But - that was on the outskirts of course.
