\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 So you would go out in the evenings quite a lot then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 
Yes. Oh yes, just wander around you know, of course - Plymouth was a - an ancient old place, town, town around the Barbican places like that well - there always something to see. I remember going up on the Hoe and s
eeing the Shanmrock race the - America, the American Cup you know, on - on - on a - on a magic lantern screen you know. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Who would be your special friends at this time, would they be people you'd know at school or would they be new people that you
'd met subsequently?
