\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Oh yes. Yes. I daresay that you - there was outside again you see, and then they were building steam pinnac}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1198299\charrsid2370612 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 es and - Admiralty boats as well as private stuff you see, so we were all engaged on similar work, where I'd just come from, in - in Plymou}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
