ll, no, it was something that was pleasurable inasmuch as you're producing something that was - that was use to other people. I mean to say - these days I don't call it boat}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1198299\charrsid2370612 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 building you know. There - this - this present system of building.
