ship, body - body board like that especially finding - you got - say - twelve planks a side or thirteen or fourteen planks aside, according to the - the width of the - the - or depth that you've got to get the boat or the ship
 - that is divided into - thirteen or fourteen parts, the same as it up and down, the stem is up and down and the stern you see so -
