\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Yes, yes, I went - I went in the dockyard.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 What were you doing there?
