\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 All salaried, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392620 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 How did you feel about that work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1141354 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 Oh I - I - I liked the - I liked the challenge really. Mind you - it was - rougher. Very very much rougher. Than working in - in a
 boat shed, in a building boats. Conditions were tot - totally different. Oh yes, you'd get out on a - on a - either a steel deck or the boards with - snow and ice and that sort of thing and you go to pick up a - a coal chisel or a - or a - a steel spanne
r, it's just like catching hold of a red hot bar you know, it was so cold Yes.
