rful weight of education, at that time. Yes, I was. But when I came up here as an improver - I went to night}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1198299\charrsid2370612 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484140\charrsid2370612 
school and - in the tech down in Gillingham, to learn Naval architecture, and - I did - quite a bit - I did a term or too. But I - but I but by then - I had - faded out you know.
